                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10271" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2594</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">248 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">保利发展：“精于战略”穿周期 “长于执行”创一流</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Poly Developments and Holdings: Strategic Mastery to Navigate Cycles，Execution Excellence to Lead the Industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王雪冬，刘黎，董大海，陶苗，朱方伟，于米</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连海事大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">董大海</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">保利发展控股集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">产业生命周期；战略类型；战略节奏；战略执行；国企专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Industry Life Cycle, Growth Strategy, Strategic Rhythm, Strategic Execution</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略是做正确的事，执行则是正确地做事，成功的企业都是战略与执行完美融合的结果。本案例聚焦于“战略与执行的关系”知识点，通过对保利发展在产业生命周期不同阶段的战略类型演变、战略节奏变化、战略执行落地的纵向过程分析，突出强调了国有企业“专业化、一体化、多元化、生态化”的战略类型顺势演变过程、“宜快则快、宜慢则慢、快慢结合”的战略节奏灵动变换特点，以及“听指挥、快执行、高协同”的长于执行特质。最终，在进阶式问题引导下，引导学员了解战略与执行的关系，掌握产业生命周期视角下的国有企业动态战略管理理论，帮助学员在知识、能力、观念更新方面实现综合提升。本案例同时回答了国有企业如何基于产业生命周期有效管理公司战略，建设中国特色现代新国企问题，为国有企业有效实施战略管理提供了案例启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Strategy pertains to doing the right things, execution involves doing things correctly. Successful enterprises adeptly merge both aspects. This case study examines the interplay between strategy and execution. Through an analysis of Poly Development&#39;s strategic shifts, rhythm adjustments, and execution methodologies across various industry life cycle phases, it illustrates how state-owned enterprises (SOEs) transform their strategies (specialization, integration, diversification and ecosystem), adapt their operational pace (accelerating, decelerating, or balancing as required), and achieve excellence in execution (complying with directives, acting swiftly, and collaborating efficiently). Guided discussions within the case study assist learners in comprehending the synergistic relationship between strategy and execution, mastering dynamic strategic management for SOEs, and enhancing their knowledge, abilities, and mindset. It also addresses how SOEs can tailor their strategies according to industry life cycles and construct contemporary SOEs with Chinese characteristics, providing practical insights for strategic management.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略与执行；战略类型；战略节奏；战略执行；产业生命周期</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
